id":"ca717e7801380d5001e75218111ecbf68980d06a","tid":388823,"uid":7138,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"讀多六年即係學藝未精啦，斷錯証好正常"},{"pid":"ffc6b39016b5027d14320577a57763630a39afaf","tid":388823,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"樣問題，難以服眾"},{"pid":"f64f6da22f3187b4bc608242dda3b69273cb8ea7","tid":388823,"uid":120753,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"根本無問題<br />\n系小小人話樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常睇睇下就變令"},{"pid":"895b622611c2d41989bd032c36955b083afd433d","tid":388823,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀多六年即係學藝未精啦，斷錯証好正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3659ae6ee73c22eda349493710d93f25adfd27d4","tid":388823,"uid":53037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本無問題<br />\n系小小人話樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常睇睇下就變令</blockquote><br />\n系你老母"},{"pid":"ac5ca232663b23de476cf4518a6bc5a364e71549","tid":388823,"uid":64969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻駁嘴</span></span>"},{"pid":"b828721889b794b0c014c8d63589531b54b6cb76","tid":388823,"uid":59575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"佢無問題呀..係佢老豆老母有問題咋馬..生成佢咁"},{"pid":"33cb7a533da25e42b21197547750939fbee57bbb","tid":388823,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>還要讀多6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫咩撚野牙醫</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係獸醫既牙科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有咗牙醫牌，再修專科，未有牌，話要讀多6年，但牙醫學院本身係四年到六年制；即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加拿大七年<br />\n眾所周知，加拿大報讀牙科或醫科，申請者都須先持有4年生命學科的本科學位，或最少完成3年大學課程。取錄到牙醫學院後之後，再要修讀4年，假如繼續深造專科牙醫，又是3-6年。<br />\n上網睇<br />\n所以一係佢year 1，一係佢深造緊</blockquote><br />\n唔同英制，冇人會咁講；因加拿大頭個個四年本科學位係普通本科學位來，唔係牙科專有，乜人都會讀，你畢咗業，考個牙醫學院公開試，就入學牙醫學院，去報教師學院，就教師，醫學院，咪醫生，唔讀，咪做野囉。"},{"pid":"828aa8adad82758d5bddfff9ec1dc6e027369c8b","tid":388823,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"掀唇露齦與謀必洩"},{"pid":"ee14cfb14cfe20cff0887ec5ffa7f5283ce8810a","tid":388823,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e758458adba1ca1fd451d04958dbd93e89f8e4","tid":388823,"uid":94837,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"佢老竇咁疊水 我係條仔既話<br />\n隻猩猩係弱智我都話無問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6bd2c2fd13fbb5a3aa75580f29026a88b5eb3f","tid":388823,"uid":56432,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:21:09.000Z","msg":"好明顯佢生活係一個國王的新衣嘅世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人直截了當講出事實批評佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢而家好不知所措<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe74afc759389caec52b07f1e20b4669393075e","tid":388823,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0